import React from 'react';
import { Grid, Paper, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import { LineChart, Line, XAxis, YAxis, CartesianGrid, Tooltip, Legend } from 'recharts';

const Dashboard = () => {
  const performanceData = [
    { time: '00:00', cpu: 65, memory: 45, network: 30 },
    { time: '04:00', cpu: 70, memory: 50, network: 35 },
    { time: '08:00', cpu: 80, memory: 60, network: 45 },
    { time: '12:00', cpu: 85, memory: 65, network: 50 },
  ];

  return (
    <Grid container spacing={3}>
      <Grid item xs={12}>
        <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>System Overview</Typography>
      </Grid>
      
      <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
        <Paper sx={{ p: 2 }}>
          <Typography variant="h6">Firewall</Typography>
          <Typography>Status: Active</Typography>
          <Typography>Throughput: 1.2 Gbps</Typography>
          <Typography>Active Connections: 1,234</Typography>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>

      <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
        <Paper sx={{ p: 2 }}>
          <Typography variant="h6">Switch</Typography>
          <Typography>Status: Active</Typography>
          <Typography>Port Utilization: 75%</Typography>
          <Typography>Error Rate: 0.01%</Typography>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>

      <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
        <Paper sx={{ p: 2 }}>
          <Typography variant="h6">Windows Server</Typography>
          <Typography>Status: Active</Typography>
          <Typography>CPU Usage: 45%</Typography>
          <Typography>Memory Usage: 60%</Typography>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>

      <Grid item xs={12}>
        <Paper sx={{ p: 2 }}>
          <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>Performance Metrics</Typography>
          <LineChart width={1000} height={300} data={performanceData}>
            <CartesianGrid strokeDasharray="3 3" />
            <XAxis dataKey="time" />
            <YAxis />
            <Tooltip />
            <Legend />
            <Line type="monotone" dataKey="cpu" stroke="#8884d8" />
            <Line type="monotone" dataKey="memory" stroke="#82ca9d" />
            <Line type="monotone" dataKey="network" stroke="#ffc658" />
          </LineChart>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  );
};

export default Dashboard;
